.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH DELPHI-NOISE 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
noise \- Add colour noise overlay to artwork
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBnoise\fR [\fB\-\-opacity\fR] [\fB\-\-scale\fR] [\fB\-\-seed\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIIMAGES\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Add colour noise overlay to artwork
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-opacity\fR \fI<OPACITY>\fR [default: 0.15]
Opacity 0.0 – 1.0
.TP
\fB\-\-scale\fR \fI<SCALE>\fR [default: 1.0]
Noise scale (1.0 = 1px grain)
.TP
\fB\-\-seed\fR \fI<SEED>\fR
Random seed (default: random)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIIMAGES\fR]

